  <brief_title>Mapracorat Ophthalmic Formulation in Subjects With Allergic Conjunctivitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose Ranging Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Mapracorat Ophthalmic Formulation, in Subjects With Allergic Conjunctivitis Compared to Vehicle in a Conjunctival Allergen Challenge (CAC).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
