  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the dose response, and efficacy of Mapracorat
      ophthalmic formulation compared to its vehicle for the prevention of symptoms and signs
      associated with allergic conjunctivitis using a conjunctival allergen challenge (CAC) model.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
